### Sprint Completion

- [ ] All sprint tasks complete and merged
- [ ] No open PRs targeting this release
- [ ] CHANGELOG updated with release notes

### Quality Gates

- [ ] Quality gate passes on all services
- [ ] `{{LINT_CMD}}` clean across all packages
- [ ] `{{TYPE_CHECK_CMD}}` clean across all packages
- [ ] `{{BUILD_CMD}}` succeeds for production target

### Tests

- [ ] All unit tests pass (`{{TEST_CMD}}`)
- [ ] All integration tests pass
- [ ] E2E tests pass critical paths on staging
- [ ] No skipped tests without documented justification

### Database

- [ ] Database migrations tested on staging
- [ ] Migration rollback tested and verified
- [ ] Seed data excluded from production migration
- [ ] Backup taken before migration

### Environment

- [ ] Environment variables documented and configured for production
- [ ] No secrets or credentials in codebase
- [ ] `.env.example` updated with any new variables
- [ ] Health check endpoints responding on staging

### Bugs

- [ ] No P0 (critical) bugs in bug inventory
- [ ] No P1 (high) bugs in bug inventory
- [ ] Known issues documented in release notes

### Performance

- [ ] Performance acceptable -- page load < 3s on target devices
- [ ] API response times within SLA (< {{API_RESPONSE_TARGET}}ms)
- [ ] No memory leaks detected in extended testing
- [ ] Database queries optimized (no N+1, proper indexing)

### Security

- [ ] Security scan clean -- no critical vulnerabilities
- [ ] Auth and authorization tested for all roles
- [ ] Input validation in place on all endpoints
- [ ] CORS configuration correct for production
- [ ] Rate limiting configured on public endpoints

### Deployment

- [ ] Monitoring and alerts configured
- [ ] Rollback plan documented and tested
- [ ] On-call schedule confirmed for post-deploy window

